tspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102703/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_use-pic-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-260028\">all photos c. Somewear</figcaption></figure><p>Connected to the low orbit Iridium satellite network, the palm-sized device connects to your phone with an app that gives you: global SMS texting, 7-day weather forecasting, now publicly accessible continuous location/movement tracking (via shared web link), and the new ability to log &amp; share <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/25/wahoo-elemnt-bolt-gps-strikes-back-w-color-screen-increased-storage-usb-c-charging-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">onX</a> waypoints of interest on the go – all without access to conventional mobile phone network coverage. Even without the phone, the device connects you to <a href=\"https://www.geosresponse.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GEOS/ IERCC</a> worldwide for one-touch emergency SOS response calling in the closest search &amp; rescue team.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions.jpg\" alt=\"Somewear Global Hotspot satellite tracker get lower pricing more functionality\" width=\"1400\" height=\"750\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-297x159.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-800x429.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-120x64.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-768x411.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-696x373.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-1068x572.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-784x420.jpg 784w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-297x159.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-800x429.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-120x64.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-768x411.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-696x373.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-1068x572.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102714/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_app-functions-784x420.jpg 784w\"></a></p><p>What’s new, Somewear has also added the ability to adjust how frequently it pings satellites for location tracking, anywhere between 10-30 minutes, and you can even now turn tracking on &amp; off directly from the device. That is said to extend battery life noticeably, beyond the 10 days you’ll already get at the most frequent 10min interval. The device now also gets Smart Routing that lets your phone try to establish cellular communication through its own antennae, before the device starts pinging satellites – another device battery &amp; data saving feature.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices.jpg\" alt=\"Somewear Global Hotspot satellite tracker get lower pricing more functionality\" width=\"1500\" height=\"550\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-297x109.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-800x293.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-768x282.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-696x255.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-1068x392.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-1145x420.jpg 1145w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-297x109.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-800x293.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-768x282.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-696x255.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-1068x392.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/26102709/Somewear-Global-Hotspot-satellite-tracker-get-lower-pricing-more-functionality_new-prices-1145x420.jpg 1145w\"></a></p><p>One of the biggest updates here is simply lower pricing. Now down to $280 for the Somewear Global Hotspot itself, that’s come into the realm of pricing cyclists are paying for premium GPS cycling computers. (<em>Coincidentally the same price as the newly updated color <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/25/wahoo-elemnt-bolt-gps-strikes-back-w-color-screen-increased-storage-usb-c-charging-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wahoo Element Bolt</a>.</em>) Plus, it’s 20% cheaper than when Somewear launched the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/25/wahoo-elemnt-bolt-gps-strikes-back-w-color-screen-increased-storage-usb-c-charging-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tracker/communicator</a>.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p>You still have to pay ongoing fees for connectivity, just like your cell phone. Those costs haven’t really gone down, staying most affordable if you commit to a $100/yr contract. But Somewear has made it clear that their other options can be activated a month at a time for a much lower cost if you aren’t adventuring year-round, plus they’ll tack on a free month if you pick one of the more expensive plans for a full year contract.</p><h3>Somewear Global Hotspot satellite tracking &amp; communication device</h3><p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/somewear-global-hotspot-geos-device-tracker-location-sharing-explore-safety-ios-android.jpg\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/somewear-global-hotspot-geos-device-tracker-location-sharing-explore-safety-ios-android.jpg\"></p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>The 114g device is available direct from Somewear and connects via BLE with iOS &amp; Android devices for full satellite functionality, and 100% global coverage. The device is IP68 rated, temperature &amp; impact-resistant, and it floats.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.somewearlabs.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>SomewearLabs.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b594010b56b4a2380be0b744cb9e64ae78073b0333bc78fe71ce662c8355a861","category":"Cycling"}